{"tid":463863,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d囡囡成日翹腳 仲要翹完左腳 蹺右腳？？","createTime":"2017-11-10T02:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T09:42:58.000Z","uid":10338,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f633ad21069332b5147685e950bb5dec4c03ac","tid":463863,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 點忍呀 特別係果個係你個fd<br />\n坐隔離 係要翹腳 唔望又好蝕底<br />\n望又好似好變態 被佢發現咪仆街<br />\n但d囡囡隻腳又白又滑 睇到真係吞晒口水<br />\n特別係肥肥白白有肉地既大脾<br />\n真係好想用手瘋狂咁摸<br />\n再擺塊面瘋狂咁摔落去呀<br />\n再用條痢由小腿一路奶上去呀 <br />\n屌 有時仲唔知係咪有心玩野 ff到咁上下<br />\n明明翹翹下左腳 又要轉腳 翹右腳 扮史朗東莎咩 真係頂唔撚順呀 要丁完左腳 丁右腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/102023_39a2bd57f49a7b509b66e96c35e7512d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F102023_39a2bd57f49a7b509b66e96c35e7512d.jpg&h=4c511ebe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b401f8b7c3b067ffc915b063c9aa066e3db39000","tid":463863,"uid":87506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"隻腳會攰架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930cb1fd5bffd988852ddeabc59ab65732dfddda","tid":463863,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6ee3ea595cbbfd6c75847880a31521937456033","tid":463863,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LSww87NH5tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLSww87NH5tw&d=8o8IpGvZIrFUzz0L7rZ4FhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b380db2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LSww87NH5tw</a>"},{"pid":"f7f2f47eb4f884fda28077b2792491e594b199ee","tid":463863,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br 